<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Core Platform - Sindika</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .glow-effect {
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-indigo-50 min-h-screen">
         <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-20 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <div class="inline-block mb-6">
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Komponen Inti Platform</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
                Platform <span class="gradient-text">Sindika</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Ekosistem teknologi terintegrasi yang dirancang khusus untuk transformasi digital gereja modern
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <a href="/sindi-ai" class="card-hover glow-effect block p-10 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/60 rounded-3xl shadow-xl group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">SINDI AI</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Asisten analisis data cerdas untuk memahami tren jemaat dan membuat laporan pelayanan yang komprehensif</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-blue-600 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">
                    Pelajari lebih lanjut
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>

            <a href="/storage-api" class="card-hover glow-effect block p-10 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/60 rounded-3xl shadow-xl group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 19a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h4l2 2h4a2 2 0 012 2v1M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2v-5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Storage API</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Penyimpanan terpusat yang aman untuk semua dokumen gereja, dari notulensi majelis hingga materi pembinaan</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-emerald-600 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">
                    Pelajari lebih lanjut
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>

            <a href="/e-warta" class="card-hover glow-effect block p-10 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/60 rounded-3xl shadow-xl group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">E-Warta Digital</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Warta gereja digital yang terintegrasi, mudah didistribusikan, dan ramah lingkungan untuk jemaat masa kini</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-purple-600 group-hover:text-pink-600 transition-colors">
                    Pelajari lebih lanjut
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>

            <a href="/konselor-ai" class="card-hover glow-effect block p-10 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/60 rounded-3xl shadow-xl group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">AI Konselor</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Asisten pastoral virtual untuk dukungan awal yang aman, anonim, dan terpercaya bagi jemaat yang membutuhkan</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-amber-600 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">
                    Pelajari lebih lanjut
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-20 text-center">
            <div class="inline-block p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
                <p class="text-white text-lg font-medium mb-4">Siap untuk transformasi digital gereja Anda?</p>
                <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-white text-indigo-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all">
                    Mulai Sekarang
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>